						               													<description>As the Heroes close in on the Villain that has been terrorizing Shadowbrook, they will need to keep their wits about them and use every strength they can muster to overcome the evil that stalks them. There can be no turning back now, and no holding back in their fight for survival!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This 24 card Game Supplement for A Touch of Evil adds a new dimension to the game and an entirely new mechanic in the form of Hero Upgrade cards. Now Heroes can use the Investigation and Event cards they've found on their hunt for the creature to 'Level Up', unlocking stat bonuses and a new Ability. Each of the 24 cards in this set is unique and applies to a specific Hero, covering all of the Heroes released to date from the base game, Something Wicked, The Coast, Hero Pack 1 and Hero Pack 2.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
